snippet.description:
This video shows you how to pronounce Doppelgänger.
SUBSCRIBE for how to pronounce more http://full.sc/13hW2AR

In fiction and folklore, a doppelgänger or doppelganger is a paranormal double of a living person. Doppelganger also describes the sensation of having glimpsed oneself in one's own peripheral vision with no chance of the supposed phenomenon having been a reflection.

How to Pronounce Doppelgänger | PronunciationManual
http://www.youtube.com/pronunciationmanual
